      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my reliable daily driver. It's in great shape and has been so dependable for me\u2014honestly, it still runs like a dream! I've taken good care of it, and it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. I'm hoping for a quick sale, so I've set a really fair price. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person!",
