    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is a true driver\u2019s car, equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback expected from this platform. While presenting with minor cosmetic patina reflective of its mileage, the powertrain is in excellent health, delivering linear acceleration and a visceral acoustic profile up to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
