    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior presents beautifully in its original paint, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical signs of careful highway use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape; the leather upholstery remains supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all digital displays and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. I have followed the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule religiously, with a recent synthetic oil change and a full brake inspection completed just last month. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It drives straight, quiet, and reliable. Sale includes two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
